title: Impact Of Alex Smith To Washington Trade, Gronk's Availability (Football 01/31)
description:
Will Brinson and Nick Kostos bring you another edition of the Pick Six podcast, not from Radio Row in Minnesota, but from undisclosed locations, to discuss the impact of the Alex Smith-KC to Washington trade-along with Rob Gronkowski's availability for Super Bowl LII on Sunday.
